@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "الصفحة الرئيسية";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<style>
    body { direction: rtl; font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; }


</style>

<div dir="rtl">
<div class="relative flex min-h-screen w-full flex-col overflow-x-hidden">
<!-- Navigation -->
<header class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-background-light/80 dark:bg-background-dark/80 backdrop-blur-md px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40 py-3">
<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary">
<div class="size-8 flex items-center justify-center bg-primary rounded-lg text-white">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-2xl">rocket_launch</span>
</div>
<h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">صلاحلي</h2>
</div>
<nav class="hidden md:flex flex-1 justify-end gap-10 items-center ml-8">
<a class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#features">الخدمات</a>
<a class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#pricing">الأسعار</a>
<a class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#about">من نحن</a>
</nav>
<button class="flex min-w-[100px] cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-lg h-10 px-5 bg-primary text-white text-sm font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary/20">احجز الآن</button>
</div>
</header>
<main class="flex-1">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40 py-16 md:py-24">
<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:w-1/2">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
<span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary w-fit">جديد: تأمين المنزل متاح الآن!</span>
<h1 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">صيانة منزلك أصبحت بسيطة <span class="text-primary">لكل بيت</span></h1>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-[540px]">احصل على صيانة منزلك بواسطة محترفين معتمدين في القاهرة والجيزة. سريع، موثوق، وبضغطة زر واحدة. "خليها علينا".</p>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
<button class="flex min-w-[140px] cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-lg h-12 px-6 bg-primary text-white text-base font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-primary/25">ابدأ الآن</button>
<button class="flex min-w-[140px] cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-lg h-12 px-6 bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-base font-bold tracking-wide hover:bg-slate-300 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-all border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700">تعرف علينا</button>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
<div class="flex -space-x-2">
<div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full border-2 border-background-light bg-slate-300"></div>
<div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full border-2 border-background-light bg-slate-400"></div>
<div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-full border-2 border-background-light bg-slate-500"></div>
</div>
<p>انضم لآلاف الأسر التي تثق في صلاحلي لصيانة منازلهم يومياً.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full">
<div class="relative w-full aspect-square md:aspect-video lg:aspect-square bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl group">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/20 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Professional technician providing home maintenance services" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCfOgRMc84njvKXSVCuolgKPB_5R4iLgZWDYAF_OZ7dErs68LQydzKeITvCndOcHePyi70onbXzedpC5Bu9LOTE-OD4fQRQOxgp0ZPhBDe9dnBRGIUk3j-1VKuRSKDIZNmAMlZpLJ25ydwntcoX5X9erKcQWJTdLwY9P-QY5I8ynzL0E1Hcl8Fzci1EuSbDQcVd1MNi6e9vC1DOBrc3QCM5rPn4Dps2YHfM6aAmEpGu24G1iq6-9f2Vx8vK8bUwu5zxBUssB2ovy9U"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Social Proof -->
<section class="border-y border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-background-dark/50 py-12">
<div class="px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40">
<p class="text-slate-400 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-center mb-10 uppercase">موثوقون من قبل أكثر من 5,000 عائلة في مصر</p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-12 md:gap-20 opacity-50 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500"><span class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">سوديك</span><span class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">إعمار</span><span class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">ماونتن فيو</span><span class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">أوراسكوم</span><span class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">بالم هيلز</span></div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Features Section -->
<section class="px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40 py-24 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-background-dark" id="features">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-12">
<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 max-w-[720px]">
<h2 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight">لماذا تختار صلاحلي؟</h2>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-lg font-normal leading-relaxed">نحن نجمع بين التكنولوجيا الحديثة وخدمات الصيانة التقليدية. لا مزيد من العناء مع "صنايعية" غير موثوقين.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<!-- Feature 1 -->
<div class="group flex flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-8 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 transition-all duration-300">
<div class="flex items-center justify-center size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-2xl">verified_user</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold leading-tight">محترفون معتمدون</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">كل فني لدينا خضع لفحص السجل الجنائي ومدرب على أعلى مستوى لضمان أفضل جودة لمنزلك.</p>
</div>
<a class="mt-auto text-primary text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all" href="#">تعرف على المزيد <span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-sm">verified_user</span></a>
</div>
<!-- Feature 2 -->
<div class="group flex flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-8 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 transition-all duration-300">
<div class="flex items-center justify-center size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-2xl">payments</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold leading-tight">أسعار ثابتة</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">أسعار شفافة ومسبقة. لا تكاليف مخفية أو مفاوضات محرجة. ادفع بسهولة عبر فوري أو البطاقة البنكية.</p>
</div>
<a class="mt-auto text-primary text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all" href="#">تعرف على المزيد <span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-sm">payments</span></a>
</div>
<!-- Feature 3 -->
<div class="group flex flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50 p-8 hover:border-primary/50 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/5 transition-all duration-300">
<div class="flex items-center justify-center size-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-2xl">handyman</span>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
<h3 class="text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100 text-xl font-bold leading-tight">ضمان الخدمة</h3>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">نحن نضمن جودة عملنا. جميع الخدمات تأتي مع ضمان لمدة 30 يوماً لتنعم براحة بال تامة.</p>
</div>
<a class="mt-auto text-primary text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2 transition-all" href="#">تعرف على المزيد <span class="material-symbols-outlined !text-sm">handyman</span></a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Pricing CTA -->
<section class="px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40 py-24" id="pricing">
<div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-primary p-8 md:p-16">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-20 -mr-20 size-80 rounded-full bg-white/10 blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-20 -ml-20 size-80 rounded-full bg-white/10 blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-8">
